Transcription.Text: The wail should have been despairing; but it's eerie note, even in it's senseless gaggling babble, was jubilant, triumphant. Chapter 7. Happy faces and an exigency. Returning to some degree of consciousness, Steve found himself slumped in a chair trying to sha and blink away the mind-deading mists of hypnotic trance.
